<figureCitation box="[663,723,293,318]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–3" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1840,1865]" captionTargetBox="[161,1425,715,1804]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1435,705,1815]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–3. Archedontia agnesae, gen. n., sp. n., moth and genital morphology. 1. Archedontia agnesae, gen. n., sp. n. (Paratype). 2. Archedontia agnesae, gen. n., sp. n., male genitalia (Holotype). 3. Female genitalia of Archedontia agnesae (Paratype)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687724" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3687724/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="276">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
